verbose_text: Whereas GFT505 did not significantly reduce 2-h plasma glucose levels after the OGTT (effect size 0.52 mmol/L [95% one sided CI -infinity to 0.61], P = 0.18), small but significant reductions in FPG (-0.37 mmol/L [-infinity to -0.10], P = 0.01) and fructosamine (-9.46 mumol/L [-infinity to -0.60], P = 0.02) were observed in the GFT505 group.
